Type anything in the address bar and you get search results offered by SearchZubi.

By clicking "Add to chrome", I accept and agree to install SearchZubi extension and setting Chromeâ„¢ default search to that provided by the service. Search results will be powered by Bing.

1) Click on the three horizontal lines icon in the upper right-hand corner of your Chrome browser.

2) Go to "Settings".

3) In the menu that appears click on "Extensions".

4) From the list of installed Extensions, find "SearchZubi".

5) Click on "REMOVE".

6) Close your browser completely and reopen it. "SearchZubi" should be removed from your Chrome browser.
